{"tid":2311954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一貓隻對新冠病毒測試呈陽性反應","createTime":"2020-12-04T12:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T13:04:04.000Z","uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"47c4092ba1c0a457a5ff0e106f2ad25182ff4733","tid":2311954,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:47:52.000Z","msg":"一貓隻對新冠病毒測試呈陽性反應<br />\n漁護署發言人表示，該署接收的一隻貓隻，其樣本對新型冠狀病毒病病毒的測試呈陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n有關個案涉及一隻居於東涌的混種短毛貓，由於其畜養人為新型冠狀病毒病確診個案的密切接觸者，貓隻於周二被送到漁護署接受檢疫。該署為其抽取的樣本對病毒測試呈陽性反應，但該貓隻現時沒有任何與新型冠狀病毒病相關的病徵。<br />\n<br />\n漁護署會繼續為該貓隻進行密切監察及反覆測試。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2654300/%E4%B8%80%E8%B2%93%E9%9A%BB%E5%B0%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E5%91%88%E9%99%BD%E6%80%A7%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2654300%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B2%2593%25E9%259A%25BB%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E5%2591%2588%25E9%2599%25BD%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2587%2589&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=58ef751e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2654300/%E4%B8%80%E8%B2%93%E9%9A%BB%E5%B0%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E5%91%88%E9%99%BD%E6%80%A7%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89</a>"},{"pid":"76bf7217c0ced7ac69c371c9b276292a95de7105","tid":2311954,"uid":98473,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:48:34.000Z","msg":"隻貓會唔會跳唔過1cm"},{"pid":"192c0c92e9e05b06473ce65a3816cfc104f0f6b8","tid":2311954,"uid":76221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b86ac7a6e7fc4a6cc2826d47ef8d4df0462a4a9","tid":2311954,"uid":63154